558
00:35:50,873 --> 00:35:54,832
Vernon, over there...

559
00:35:54,910 --> 00:35:56,844
was in on the hit.

560
00:35:59,081 --> 00:36:01,015
That was good.

561
00:36:01,083 --> 00:36:04,177
Yeah, he heard
everything we said.

562
00:36:04,253 --> 00:36:07,245
[Hannah ] Come on, Teach.
I want you to dance with me.

563
00:36:07,323 --> 00:36:09,848
- No.
- Come on.

564
00:36:13,829 --> 00:36:18,289
So I've been rereading
Arsonist's Daughter.

565
00:36:18,367 --> 00:36:21,632
It's so beautiful, Grady.

566
00:36:21,704 --> 00:36:24,002
It's so natural.

567
00:36:24,073 --> 00:36:27,042
It's like all of your sentences
always existed, just...

568
00:36:27,109 --> 00:36:30,078
waiting for up there in style
heaven for you to fetch them down.

569
00:36:31,914 --> 00:36:33,074
I thank you.

