Good morning, boys.

717
00:48:08,833 --> 00:48:11,631
- Good morning, James.
- Good morning.

718
00:48:11,702 --> 00:48:14,262
[ Whispering ]
Jimmy, Jimmy, Jimmy.

719
00:48:14,338 --> 00:48:16,272
I'm gonna take a shower.

720
00:48:16,340 --> 00:48:20,640
@@ [ Whistling]

721
00:48:20,711 --> 00:48:22,975
- Prof. Tripp?
- Hmm?

722
00:48:23,047 --> 00:48:25,106
How did I get here last night?

723
00:48:25,182 --> 00:48:27,377
No one knows where you live,
James.

